comments.body:
I am able to reproduce the issue, same for the Ti.UI.ListView:
{code:js}
        var data = [ { properties: {title : 'Bashful', hasDetail: true}}];
 
        var win = Ti.UI.createWindow( {
            backgroundColor : 'white'
        } );
 
        var searchBar = Ti.UI.createSearchBar();
 
        var tableView = Ti.UI.createListView( {
            backgroundColor : '#999',
            searchView : searchBar,
            sections : [Ti.UI.createListSection({items: data})],
            top : 150,
            bottom : 150,
            left : 150,
            right : 150
        } );
 
        win.add( tableView);
        win.open();

{code}

PR (master) : https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/pull/9635
PR (7_0_X) : https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/pull/9657
Test Case1 -

{code:java}
       var data = [ { properties: {title : 'Bashful', hasDetail: true}}];
 
        var win = Ti.UI.createWindow( {
